TableDefinition.DatabaseQuery: select CONVERT(varchar, dpib010.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', dpib010.naam_samen + ', ' + dpib010.e_roepnaam as 'vol_nm', e_vrlt, dpib010.e_roepnaam, dpib010.vrvg_samen, dpib010.naam_samen, func_kd, func_oms, oe_kort_nm, oe_vol_nm, indnst_dt, uitdnst_dt From dpib010 inner join dpic300 on dpic300.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr inner join dpib023 on dpib023.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr left join dpic351 on dpic351.func_kd = dpic300.primfunc_kd order by dpib010.pers_nr

select distinct oe_kort_nm, oe_vol_nm From dpib010 inner join dpic300 on dpic300.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr inner join dpib023 on dpib023.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr left join dpic351 on dpic351.func_kd = dpic300.primfunc_kd order by oe_kort_nm, oe_vol_nm

select distinct func_kd, func_oms From dpib010 inner join dpic300 on dpic300.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr inner join dpib023 on dpib023.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr left join dpic351 on dpic351.func_kd = dpic300.primfunc_kd order by func_kd, func_oms
